name: El primer escalon
description:
If the ladder is the symbol of patience, I live on the first step.


The memory of his youth washes a little dust from his heart, the desperation to become the first, made him lose his way and when he wanted to realize he was still standing in the same place as when he started. I forget that the important thing is not to get there faster, but farther. Now he is looking to get out of the limbo in which he got trapped.
